2016-01-17 Alfred E. Heggestad <aeh@db.org>

	* Version 0.4.17

	* GIT URL: https://github.com/alfredh/baresip.git
	* GIT tag: v0.4.17
	* NOTE: Requires libre v0.4.14 or later
	        Requires librem v0.4.7 or later

